dungeonGame.title: Dungeon Game
dungeonGame.description: It is a game made only in Html , Css and JavaScript . It can be moved with the arrow keys of the keyboard or with the cross buttons, it consists of 3 levels where you have to look for the key and escape from the level without being reached by the monsters. To play you have to turn on the gameboy.

pikemons.title: Pikemons
pikemons.description: This is my first Full Stack application, it is made using data from the 'pokeapi' API to search for existing pokemons, in it you will find 40 preloaded pokemons but you can search for more, create your own pokemons, see the characteristics of each pokemon and have different ones filter types.

extrimianDapp.title: Extriman Dapp - Test
extrimianDapp.description: This project is a Dapp, for an Extrimian application test, that communicates with a smart contract deployed on an ethereum blockchain testnet network. The project connects with the Metamask account of the person using the app to be able to show the first 10 transactions made with the account, the transactions are obtained from the Rinkeby API. The app saves the account in the blockchain and changes it when connecting a new account.
